# Tuned Yota — Wix → new-site migration redirects (301).
# Old www URLs already 301 to non-www (Netlify domain redirect); these map
# the old Wix slugs to the matching new pages so Google transfers ranking
# signals instead of landing on 404s. Model-specific rules first, then
# static pages, then catch-alls (first match wins).

